{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The Haunted Keepsake</i> is a story-driven horror game that puts players in the shoes of an investigative reporter unraveling the eerie mystery of the Whitlock family tragedy. Decades ago, a deadly fire claimed the lives of a mother and son, leaving the father, John Whitlock, devastated and bent on vengeance. In his fury, he unleashed a curse bound to an heirloom doll\u2014a keepsake that fuels the land\u2019s restless spirits to this day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Locals claim that anyone who trespasses is haunted by whispers and sightings, while a protective force wards off outsiders. It\u2019s up to you to uncover the truth: find the cursed doll, journey to the Whitlock gravesite, and attempt to break the curse under the night sky. But beware\u2014the spirits aren\u2019t easily appeased, and they\u2019re determined to keep intruders away. Can you end the Whitlock curse, or will you become another ghost in the story of <i>The Haunted Keepsake</i>?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316340/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732026862","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316340/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732026862","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316340/95928410381f88fa7e4054fe025114af7511381e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732026862","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316340/95928410381f88fa7e4054fe025114af7511381e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732026862","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The Haunted Keepsake</i> is a story-driven horror game that puts players in the shoes of an investigative reporter unraveling the eerie mystery of the Whitlock family tragedy. Decades ago, a dea